  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He also explained to me that-- he didn't give me any specifics where we are going to move.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But ultimately, he told me that our, our mission is going to be to-- towards-- toward Germany, within Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And specifically, he based himself off my knowledge of German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he told me also that, in the beginning, we are going to be moved around between Lithuania and Latvia, whereby my Lithuanian came handy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About-- at that time, about five languages, right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, he was very friendly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he gave me-- before recruiting me, he gave me a-- like, about three weeks of time because he had to recruit some other people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he gave me some leeway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And right away, what I did is, I had some relatives who were-- who, who were stationed in Kovno.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were homeless, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't have where to stay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, being already a, a, a, a, a future soldier in the-- in the army, I had certain, certain protections and certain powers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whereby, I found a, a nice apartment, and I housed them in that apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And plus the fact I told them that-- and, and this apartment was precisely in the vicinity where I used to live before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was right in the center of Kaunas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Time was going very fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in a matter of a few weeks, I was-- I was taken to the-- to, to the army barracks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They sent me-- in the beginning when they gave me the-- a very expedient and fast training, it was very, very harsh in, in, in a certain way.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But of course, after what we have-- what we have experienced in our life, I mean, this was-- this was nothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
